text: Ayuchevo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Ayuchevsky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 297 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 30 km from Sterlitamak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Ayuchevo
